@node "How_To_Get" "How to get AmigaTNC"

 How to get it
 =============

 Internet
 ========

My packet radio BBS sysop offers WWW-URL space for his users. You can get
AmigaTNC from:

URL   http://members.aol.com/rt0bbs/users/sp7ock/amigatnc.html

 Aminet
 ======

Updates of AmigaTNC will be uploaded onto Aminet as soon as possible. Look at
comm/misc for recent updates.

 Mail
 ====

You can order AmigaTNC by mail, too. YOU ONLY GET REPLY IF YOU SEND ME A
ENVELOPE WITH YOUR ADDRESS ON IT WHICH IS POST PAID. THE ONLY JOB I WILL DO IS
TO COPY AMIGATNC ON YOUR DISK (WHICH YOU SEND ME) , PUT IT IN YOUR ENVELOPE
(WHICH YOU SEND ME,TOO) AND BRING IT TO THE POST OFFICE. If no German postage
stamps are available, you can hide GERMAN! cash in the envelope (DON'T BLAME
ME IF CASH IS LOST AND YOU DON'T GET A REPLY). If you add your PR-Mail
address, I can send you a mail, if something is wrong (e.g. not enough money,
disk error...). If everything is OK, you will get answer within 1-4 weeks.
@endnode

