 Looking for translators
 =======================

I'm looking for translators for my AmigaTNC.guide. If you want to translate
AmigaTNC to your native language, please contact me. If your language isn't
already translated you will get a reply that you can start to translate.
Please don't start translating before my reply to avoid double work of
different translators.
@endnode

